trans-unit.source: A simple implementation of the OWL2 RL Profile, as well as a basic RDFS inference, on top of RDFLib. Based mechanical forward chaining. The distribution contains:
trans-unit.target: 在RDFLib的基础上,简单实现OWL2 RL Profile,以及基本的RDFS推理。基于机械前向链。该发行版包含。
